OL,6,FWelsh Water says the company preparing
OL,7,Ffor a new investment period for 2025-
OL,8,F30, which will see a step change in
OL,9,Finvestment. More than #4bn will be
OL,10,Finvested in services including #2.5bn
OL,11,Fon projects to improve the environment.
OL,13,FIt says the price increase comes after
OL,14,Fa period of fifteen years when the
OL,15,Fcompany kept price rises below the
OL,16,Frate of inflation. It says customers
OL,17,Fwill now pay an average of #1.75 a day
OL,18,Ffor drinking water that is
OL,19,Fconsistently ranked as equal highest
OL,20,Fquality in the world.
